::Wash [nobr]
<<set _loc to $gamelocation>>
<<set _n = $ui.npc>>
<<if $lastNpc>>
    <p>_n.name joins you in the shower and you two wash yourselves.</p> 
    <p>You both could hardly keep your hands off each other but eventually you are both squeaky clean.</p>

<<else>>
    <p>You take a nice hot shower.</p>
    <p>Soon you're clean.</p>
<</if>>

<<link "Finish Shower" _loc>><</link>>